#### Send a Message
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8089/a2a/server \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "message/send",
    "params": {
      "message": {
        "role": "user",
        "parts": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "kind": "text",
            "text": "Hello, A2A!"
          }
        ]
